The '''[[Pixelito/Legends|Pixelito]] Art Guild''' was a guild that specialized in art. A [[Dug/Legends|Dug]] named [[Pixolga]] claimed that painted paw prints by a tamed [[Nexu/Legends|nexu]] did not constitute true art. His accusations resulted in severe profit loss for the guild. The organization in turn posted a bounty on Pixolga's head, which was soon claimed by [[Jango Fett/Legends|Jango Fett]].

